album.title: B.o.B Presents: The Adventures of Bobby Ray

wiki.content: According to the Don't Let Me Fall Songfacts, it is not surprising that some reviewers have commented that this piano-laden cut reminds them of Coldplay, as Bobby Ray disclosed in a video interview with Rap-Up.com that the British band's AA Rush of Blood to the Head is an album he can't live without.
